HEADWORD: Sacrovertebral
<hw>Sa`cro*ver"te*bral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the sacrum and that part of
the vertebral column immediately anterior to it; <as>as, the
<ex>sacrovertebral</ex> angle</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
